parameters: I got a whisker in my eye, I can't get it out.
When my face became one big eye, I lost the ability to wink.
Or maybe you could say I'm always winking...
Hey... I got a stash of cheese. It's good stuff.
Some brie... some gouda... I even got some quality sharp cheddar.
Want some of that good stuff? The sharp stuff...
I can hook you up. $20 for two wedges...\$
Yeaah, you know it. Two wedges coming right up!
Come back tomorrow and I'll get you more...
\C[5]ARRRHHGNN!!\C[0] I made a burrito. Do you want it?
I didn't really make it. I stole it. I'm sorry.
